Q: Modify the following loop so it iterates 5 times instead 
of just once.

iterations = 1

loop do
  puts "Number of iterations = #{iterations}"
  break
end

My A:

iterations = 1

loop do
  if iterations <= 5
  puts "Number of iterations = #{iterations}"
  iterations += 1
end

LS A:

iterations = 1

loop do
  puts "Number of iterations = #{iterations}"
  iterations += 1
  break if iterations > 5
end